    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Just have to let you know that I discovered this recipe in your book, and have been in love with it ever since.  We make them frequently, most often with frozen berries, and they are quite decadent.  <br />I am in the midst of making several batches for an upcoming work meeting, and will be trying some of the new flavor combos I discovered in these comments here.  <br />This has been a fail-proof recipe for me, and I can&#39;t thank you enough for sharing it!</p>
    </div>

